OL,3,C'Much to do' on prison drug problems
OL,5,FPrison inspectors have voiced concern
OL,6,Fat progress against recommendations
OL,7,Fmade at HMP Magilligan in Co
OL,8,FLondonderry.JMore progress was found
OL,9,Fto have been made at HMP Maghaberry in
OL,10,FCo Antrim but inspectors concluded
OL,11,Fthere remains "much to do" to address
OL,12,Fpriority and key concerns identified.
OL,13,FThe conclusions come following the
OL,14,Ffirst Independent Reviews of Progress
OL,15,F(IRPs) to be carried out by Inspectors
OL,16,Fat Maghaberry and Magilligan following
OL,17,Fcritical inspection reports.
