OL,3,C'Much to do' on prison drug problems
OL,5,FThe inspectors concluded: "We do not
OL,6,Funderestimate the challenges faced by
OL,7,Fleaders in the Northern Ireland Prison
OL,8,FService and its service partners,
OL,9,Fparticularly with the current prison
OL,10,Fpopulation numbers and resource
OL,11,Fchallenges to drive improvement, and
OL,12,Fit was evident that leaders, managers
OL,13,Fand staff had taken some steps to
OL,14,Frespond to the respective inspection
OL,15,Ffindings.J"However, ambition and
OL,16,Faction are needed to support prisoners
OL,17,Fleaving custody healthier, more
OL,18,Femployable, making better choices and
OL,19,Fless likely to return to prison."
