OL,3,C'Much to do' on prison drug problems
OL,5,FJustice Minister Naomi Long said
OL,6,Finspectors play a "vital role in
OL,7,Fholding us to account and offering
OL,8,Fscrutiny and focus on issues to be
OL,9,Faddressed".JShe said prisons are
OL,10,Ffacing challenges with a rising
OL,11,Fprisoner population, many with complex
OL,12,Fneeds including addiction and poor
OL,13,Fmental health.
