OL,3,C'Much to do' on prison drug problems
OL,5,F"It is a sad fact that people in
OL,6,Fprison are more likely to have a
OL,7,Fhistory of drug use than people in the
OL,8,Fwider community," she said.J"Prison
OL,9,Fstaff work tirelessly to disrupt the
OL,10,Fflow of illegal substances into the
OL,11,Fjails, as well as supporting recovery
OL,12,Ffrom addiction.J"These issues make
OL,13,Fsupporting the vital work of
OL,14,Frehabilitation increasingly difficult."
