OL,3,C'Much to do' on prison drug problems
OL,5,FShe added: "However prisons are making
OL,6,Fprogress. Since their introduction in
OL,7,FMarch last year, the X-ray body
OL,8,Fscanners have had a major impact on
OL,9,Fstemming the flow of drugs and illegal
OL,10,Fsubstances coming into prisons. This
OL,11,Fhelps to keep both staff and prisoners
OL,12,Fsafer.J"The Prison Service is
OL,13,Fcommitted to maintaining strong
OL,14,Fpartnerships with colleagues in the
OL,15,FSouth Eastern Health and Social Care
OL,16,FTrust and the Department of Health,
OL,17,Fparticularly in seeking to disrupt the
OL,18,Ftrade of medication within prisons."
